---

This project depends on several third-party open-source fonts. They are
downloaded at install time by `scripts/install-fonts.mjs` and remain
governed by their own licenses (all OFL-compatible):

  • Noto Sans SC / Noto Serif SC      — Google, SIL OFL 1.1
  • LXGW WenKai (霞鹜文楷)            — lxgw,  SIL OFL 1.1
  • ZCOOL XiaoWei / KuaiLe /          — Google Fonts (Adobe / ZCOOL),
    QingKe HuangYou                     SIL OFL 1.1
  • Ma Shan Zheng (马善政毛笔)        — Google Fonts, SIL OFL 1.1
  • Long Cang (龙藏体)                — Google Fonts, SIL OFL 1.1
  • Liu Jian Mao Cao (柳建毛草)       — Google Fonts, SIL OFL 1.1
